Module atu.software
Package ie.atu.sw.services

Interface Examiner

All Known Implementing Classes:
ExternalExaminer, InternalExaminer
public interface Examiner
Interface representing an examiner. Defines the basic properties and methods that an examiner should have, including their name, type, and associated department.
